'''那旺·多吉·雪巴'''（{{lang-en|Nawang Dorje Sherpa}}）是一位[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]][[登山家|登山家]]和[[高山嚮導|高山嚮導]]，以[[首次登頂|首次登頂]][[道拉吉里峰|道拉吉里峰]]聞名，登過數座[[喜馬拉雅山脈|喜馬拉雅山脈]]的山峰，也是赫爾維蒂—奧地利遠征隊的成員。

== 登山 ==
* 1960 – [[道拉吉里峰|道拉吉里峰]]，與{{link-en|庫特·典保格|Kurt Diemberger}}、Peter Diener、Nima Dorje、Ernst Forrer、Albin Schelbert等人<ref name=aj_1984>{{Cite journal
  | author = Dangar, D.F.O
  | title = A Record of the First Ascents of the Fifty Highest Mountains
  | journal = Alpine Journal
  | publisher = Alpine Club
  | url = http://www.alpinejournal.org.uk/Contents/Contents_1984_files/AJ%201984%20184-187%20Dangar%20Ascents.pdf
  | year = 1984
  | volume = 89
  | pages = 184–7
  | accessdate = April 24, 2011
  | archive-date = 2016-03-04
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070416/http://www.alpinejournal.org.uk/Contents/Contents_1984_files/AJ%201984%20184-187%20Dangar%20Ascents.pdf
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>。
* 1995 - [[卓奧友峰|卓奧友峰]]，29月29日與Tomonori Harada、Shigeki Imoto、Kunga Sherpa等人<ref>{{cite journal|last=Hawley|first=Elizabeth|year=1995|title=Asia, Tibet, Cho Oyu from Tibet in the Post-Monsoon: Climbs And Expeditions|journal=American Alpine Journal|volume=69|issue=37|url=http://publications.americanalpineclub.org/articles/12199530500/Asia-Tibet-Cho-Oyu-from-Tibet-in-the-Post-Monsoon|access-date=2016-11-18|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103515/http://publications.americanalpineclub.org/articles/12199530500/Asia-Tibet-Cho-Oyu-from-Tibet-in-the-Post-Monsoon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* 1996 - [[珠穆朗瑪峰|珠穆朗瑪峰]]，東南脊路線，與{{link-en|佩特·史秋寧|Pete Schoening}}、[[阿納托利·波克里夫|阿納托利·波克里夫]]、{{link-en|史考特·費雪|Scott Fischer}}等人<ref>{{cite journal|last=Fox|first=Charlotte|year=1997|title=A Time to Live, a Time to Die|journal=American Alpine Journal|publisher=American Alpine Club Press|pages=27–36|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FattUWiYu80C&pg=PA36 }}</ref>，遭遇[[1996年聖母峰事故|山難]]。
* 2000 - 珠穆朗瑪峰，5月19日，北脊路線<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.everestsummiteersassociation.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=13%3Anepal&limitstart=4|title=Nepal|publisher=Everest Summiters Association|accessdate=4 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904195339/http://www.everestsummiteersassociation.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=13:nepal&limitstart=4|archive-date=2014-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
* 2004 - 第三度登頂珠穆朗瑪峰，隨國際遠征隊自[[南坳|南坳]]路線登頂<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adventurestats.com/tables/draft/2004summiters.htm|title=Everest South Col Route|publisher=Αdventurestats.com|accessdate=4 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905000159/http://www.adventurestats.com/tables/draft/2004summiters.htm|archive-date=2014-09-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
* 2007 - 第四度登頂珠穆朗瑪峰，隨法國遠征隊登頂<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iamsherpa.blogspot.gr/p/v-behaviorurldefaultvmlo.html|title=Himalayan sherpa|last=Gyalje Sherpa|first=Mingma|accessdate=4 September 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212530/http://iamsherpa.blogspot.gr/p/v-behaviorurldefaultvmlo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另外，他也曾攀登{{link-en|安納普納四峰|Annapurna IV}}、[[島峰|島峰]]和{{link-en|皮桑峰|Pisang Peak}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uniquetreks.com/company_info/leader1.php|title=Climbing (Expedition) Leaders|publisher=Unique Adventure International|accessdate=4 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904195814/http://www.uniquetreks.com/company_info/leader1.php|archive-date=2014-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

